com.github.robtimus.util.iterator

Interface StreamLikeIterator<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - The element type.
    All Superinterfaces:
    Iterator<E>

    public interface StreamLikeIterator<E>
extends Iterator<E>
    An Iterator that contains additional functionality similar to Stream.
    Author:
    Rob Spoor
    API Note:
    Instances of this class support the Iterator.remove() operation if the original iterator does, and no intermediate operation of this class removes support for the operation.
